<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_457_r1l6"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>Han<ex>n</ex>s</expan> . Ewrn brief vnd <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> von 
<add><ab facs="#facs_457_r1l5">der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> der habe vnd </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_457_r1l7">
<del rend="strikethrough">kauffmanſchaft wegen die Jr den ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_457_r1l8">
<del rend="strikethrough">habt </del> / darümb vvir euch vormals <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_457_r1l9"> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir wol vernomen . Vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough">die </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_457_line_1577285003413_9183">die </ab></add> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_457_r1l11">die das antrifft 
<add><ab facs="#facs_457_r1l10">vnd anheim ſind </ab></add> darumb cʒurede geſacʒt / die <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_457_r1l12">vns <expan>geantvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / daʒ die hab vnd kauffmanſchaft die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_457_r1l14">ſie vormals vor vns cʒu den heıligen behabt 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_457_r1l13">vnd </ab></add> </ab>
