<add><ab facs="#facs_457_r1l16"><expan>dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> vvir ew <expan>geſ<ex>chriben</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> Jr ſey / Alſo daʒ <expan>kein<ex>er</ex></expan> von Erffurd noch ſüſt kein ander </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_457_r1l17">auſʒman daran weder teil noch gemein niht hab . <expan>Dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_457_r1l18">daʒ Jr <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> burgern <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Jr habe vnd <expan>kauffm<ex>anſchaft</ex></expan> </ab>
