<ab facs="#facs_457_r1l23">
<add><ab facs="#facs_457_r1l24">nehſten </ab></add> monad her 
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒu vns </del> kumt So ſüllt Jr cʒu vnd von vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_457_r1l26">für vns vnd die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / vnd bey vns 
