<ab facs="#facs_457_r1l27"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ongeuerde / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>do<ex>min</ex>ıcam</expan> <expan>Trinitat<ex>em</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_457_r1l29">Anno etc xxij<hi rend="sup">o</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_457" id="227v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
